channel.title: Please help! [525] I need fremennik spiritual realm coordinates [525]
channel.description:
hello I've been searching for the coords of the fremennik spiritual realm on google for awhile, and nobody seems to know what they are. I have a few coords lists but I've search through them and can't find what i'm looking for. The spirit realm is in the quest blood runs deep. Your player dies while following a king up a ladder by rocks, and then spawns here. And i'm sure that if someone uses rsbot, or power bot, they could get the coords for me. I'm not a member, so i can't go to this location and do it myself. If you already know them, please post them to me. I am prepared to give 1m rsgp to whoever gives me the correct coords. So yeah thats it. thanks for any help. Oh and i'm using a 525 server - mast3r pkyz/codeusa.
picture of the place i'm talking about. [img]http://images.wikia.com/runescape/images/a/aa/Fremennik_spiritual_world.png[/img]
and another.. [img]http://images.wikia.com/runescape/images/c/cb/Fremennik_spiritual_realm.png[/img]
